<br>
With a heavy heart, we respect Haemish's decision to depart.  The members asked for an expeditious choice of the next guild leader so a thread for Guild Leader nominations in the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>     Policy Forum</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  (seemed a better place than the war room) has been created:<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm28.showMessage?topicID=8.topic">pub15.ezboard.com/fdagger...ID=8.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Even if you nominated or seconded someone in the meeting tonight, please do so again in the thread</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
This vote is open to all Daggers, full members and probationary.<br>
<br>
Some questions that were asked:<br>
 - Has the treasury hunt been rescheduled?<br>
 -&gt; Yes.  Trying to avoid weekends and multiple-events in a row (and avoiding Valentines) Friday the 15th, 8pm CST.  That's it's <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>      current</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> scheduled date.  However, Monday is Dagger Policy/Promotion night which will probably end quite early and we may head out to for the Treasury hunt then.<br>
<br>
 - Should we change the guild name?<br>
 -&gt;  Silver Daggers are and Silver Daggers we will remain.  Not only would it end the proud line of the Daggers and it's two previous guild leaders but, as Goethiel pointed out, (paraphrased) &quot;we're all Daggers at heart so changing the name won't mean anything.&quot;<br>
<br>
 - Should we appoint an interim guild leader?<br>
 -&gt; We will not be appointing an interim GL.  The members wished for an expeditious vote and Haemish left one <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>      big</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> honkin' void to fill that no one wants to do short-term.  Should any crisis matters come to light before the vote is ended, Belce will address them.<br>
<br>
 - Will current guild policies remain in effect during the interim? <br>
 -&gt;  Most certainly.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>      Nothing</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> is being altered until we have a GL appointed.<br>
<br>
 - When will the other officers be brought forward?<br>
 -&gt; After a new GL is seated and settled in (probably next Friday time-frame)<br>
<br>
(I know there's more but my brain is failing me -- I have a cold so my brain is off having a tax audit -- someone with notes please post some snippets to jog my brain )<br>
